Bridges ventures invests in solutions that improve physical and mental health and well-being; 
in solutions that boost skills and productivity, and strengthen pathways to employment; 
in solutions that fasten the transitioning to a lower-carbon economy; 
in solutions that increase access to opportunities and services.

As London’s official promotional organisation, London and Partners' project will attract foreign-owned SMEs to London; 
increase the growth of foreign-owned SMEs across London; enhance the productivity of foreign and London-owned SMEs by supporting collaboration with larger corporates, and enable access to international supply chains.
It seeks to create new jobs and encouarge business growth.
